subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: STATE COLLEGE, Pa., Oct. 13 (AP) — Rodney Kinlaw ran for 115 yards and a touchdown and Anthony Morelli threw for 216 yards and another score as Penn State capitalized on No. 19 Wisconsin’s mistakes in a surprisingly easy 38-7 victory Saturday.
